StatusTest.Name: TestChecked
StatusTest.Description: imported to MDM and reviewed - has substates - frozen: no further result data can be added - published: has to be available because is prerequisite to an publication

StatusTest.Name: TestRejected
StatusTest.Description: has been rejected by the executing units due to any conflict

StatusTest.Name: TestImporting
StatusTest.Description: is being imported to the MDM system

StatusTest.Name: TestDone
StatusTest.Description: has been executed and is ready for import to the MDM system

StatusTest.Name: TestClosed
StatusTest.Description: closed, no further data item can be attached.

StatusTestStep.Name: TestStepRejected
StatusTestStep.Description: has been rejected by the executing units due to any conflict

StatusTestStep.Name: TestStepImporting
StatusTestStep.Description: is being imported to the MDM system

StatusTestStep.Name: TestStepDone
StatusTestStep.Description: has been executed and is ready for import to the MDM system

StatusTestStep.Name: TestStepChecked
StatusTestStep.Description: imported to MDM and reviewed - has substates - frozen: no further result data can be added - published: has to be available because is prerequisite to an publication

Role.Name: MDMSystemAdministrator
Role.Description: system administrator of the MDM system.

Role.Name: MDMMethodsAdministrator
Role.Description: administers (creates, changes, deletes) the description patterns (MDM catalogue and MDM Templates) of the MDM system as well as the interfacing with contextual systems.

Role.Name: MDMTestPlanner
Role.Description: defines the desired boundary conditions (MDM:UnitUnderTest, MDM:TestEquipment, MDM: TestSequence) of a test.

Role.Name: MDMDataProcessor
Role.Description: retrieves data from the MDM system, generates derived data and stores it back to the MDM system

Role.Name: MDMTestConditioner
Role.Description: sets up the MDM:TestEquipment and assembles it with the MDM:UnitUnderTest to complete the Test setup for executing the MDM:TestStep

Role.Name: MDMTestObjectConditioner
Role.Description: prepares the MDM:UnitUnderTest for the MDM:TestStep.

Role.Name: MDMTestOperator
Role.Description: executes the MDM:TestSteps and generates the Test Data

Role.Name: MDMDataCustomer
Role.Description: retrieves data from the MDM system for any use

Role.Name: MDMTestReviewer
Role.Description: checks the Test results for correctness, completeness and relevancy and imports them from an external test bed system e.g. to the MDM System.

Role.Name: MDMMethodsPlanner
Role.Description: defines the standards for testing and functional design which have to be met by the tests documented in the mdm system
